當時二甲基汞是用來校正<sup>199</sup>Hg核磁共振波譜儀<ref name="ohalloran">{{cite web|url=http://chemgroups.northwestern.edu/ohalloran/HgNMRStandards/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603111937/http://chemgroups.northwestern.edu/ohalloran/HgNMRStandards/|archivedate=2013-06-03|title=<sup>199</sup>Hg NMR Standards|last1=O'Halloran|first1=Thomas V.|last2=Singer|first2=Christopher P.|publisher=Northwestern University|date=March 10, 1998|accessdate=2020-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在這次事故後，科學家重新訂立安全守則，而且不鼓勵二甲基汞的使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.osha.gov/dts/hib/hib_data/hib19980309.html|title=Hazard Information Bulletin—Dimethylmercury|publisher=[[Occupational_Safety_and_Health_Administration|Occupational Safety and Health Administration]]|date=March 9, 1998<!--Note, the website text gives an impossible 1991 date, this is taken from the url-->|access-date=May 11, 2005|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050408214930/http://www.osha.gov/dts/hib/hib_data/hib19980309.html|archive-date=2005-04-08|8=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。科學家因而發現二甲基汞能穿透聚氯乙烯和氯丁橡膠等，所以接觸時必須穿戴特別手套，以免直接接觸。
